map.upgradeText: Thuthukela ezinhlelweni zokubhaliselwe ze-$Gio manje futhi uvule amandla aphelele. Zuza izici ezithuthukisiwe, izibalo zesikhathi sangempela, nokuhlanganiswa okungenazihibe. Khuphula izinga labasebenzi bakho abakude namuhla! Chofoza ukuze uqinisekise inkokhelo yakho futhi uguqule ukusebenza kwakho.
